'''Tanfalit n Stirling''' nɣ '''Tamawaẓt n Stirling''' tga ɣ tusnakt, yat tnfalit nna yakkan agdazal n uskir n yan umḍan ummid agaman <math>n</math> iɣ yaẓ <math>n</math> i wartmi:

<math display="block">\lim_{n \to +\infty} {n\,!\over \sqrt{2 \pi n} \; \left({n}/{\rm e}\right)^{n} } = 1</math>nna nttafa tettyura ula s tɣarast ad:

<math display="block">n\,!\sim \sqrt{2\pi n}\,\left({n \over {\rm e}}\right)^n</math>maɣ <math>e</math> ɣid tga amḍan n tusnakt [[e (amḍan n tusnakt)|ikspununsyal]].
==Amzruy==
[[Brahim du Mwavr]] ad akk izwarn is yufa tanfalit ad ddaw-as:

<math display="block">n\,!\sim C\; n^{n+\frac12}\, \mathrm e^{-n}</math>

maɣ <math>C</math> tga yat timzgit tilawt (ur igaddan d amya)

Mad ifka nɣ mad izayd Stirling i tanfalit ad iga-tt atig n timzgit, iga y'as <math>C = \sqrt{2\pi n}</math> fad ad aɣ tfk asbuɣlu n <math>ln(n!)</math> i kraygat amizzwr.

